{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d1accd2d30","title":"毛泽东关于请郭沫若修改《到韶山》、《登庐山》两首诗给胡乔木的两封信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d25c086b88","index":0,"year":1959,"month":9,"day":7,"articleId":"d1accd2d30"}],"tags":[{"id":"3fd96bb002","name":"胡乔木","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2c86deafff","type":"title","text":"毛泽东关于请郭沫若修改《到韶山》、《登庐山》两首诗给胡乔木的两封信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d1accd2d30"},{"id":"f21df4f6be","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d1accd2d30"},{"id":"1e47f8f2bb","type":"appellation","text":"乔木同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d1accd2d30"},{"id":"74391b879b","type":"paragraph","text":"诗两首，请你送给郭沫若同志一阅，看有什么毛病没有?加以笔削，是为至要。主题是为了反右倾鼓干劲的，是为了惩治反党、反总路线、反大跃进、反人民公社的。主题虽好，诗意无多，只有几句较好一些的，例如“云横九派浮黄鹤”之类。诗难，不易写，经历者如鱼饮水，冷暖自知，不足为外人道也。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d1accd2d30"},{"id":"fb7e4aa68a","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东九月七日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d1accd2d30"},{"id":"eb774578c6","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d1accd2d30"},{"id":"a3f543b8e8","type":"appellation","text":"乔木同志：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d1accd2d30"},{"id":"7481e33fc3","type":"paragraph","text":"沫若同志两信都读，给了我启发。两诗又改了一点字句，请再送陈沫若一观，请他再予审改，以其意见告我为盼。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d1accd2d30"},{"id":"98792d7df4","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东九月十三日早上","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d1accd2d30"},{"id":"f2